{"tid":2197951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"受制裁捷克議員：不能進入中國，但可以隨時到台灣！","createTime":"2020-09-11T04:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T11:35:18.000Z","uid":337052,"like":568,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"566e64e6848c9e99a4f2ddacaacaea8bb33b6cdc","tid":2197951,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">曾嗆習「壞鬼」！訪台捷克參議員再酸：一中不存在</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/11/phpl5OBx9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F11%2Fphpl5OBx9.jpg&h=1729e1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨議長訪台的參議員艾斯尼班納蘭根本沒在怕，直接在飯店門前貼出寫著<span class=\"red\">「壞鬼在這間房間不受歡迎」</span>的中國領導人習近平肖像，對中國威脅做出回應。（擷取自Lum&iacute;r Aschenbrenner臉書）<br />\n<br />\n2020/09/11 11:30<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕此次隨捷克參議院議長韋德齊訪台的參議員艾斯尼班納蘭（Lum&iacute;r Aschenbrenner）曾在飯店門前貼出中國領導人習近平肖像，配上大大的中文「壞鬼在這間房間不受歡迎」強硬回擊中國威脅，昨（10日）<span class=\"red\">他在推特發文表示，自己將被禁止進入中國，但他卻可以隨時到台灣，「這證明一個中國根本不存在」。</span><br />\n<br />\n針對捷克團訪台一事，中國外交部長王毅曾恐嚇捷克「會付出代價」，艾斯尼班納蘭則直接在臉書PO出飯店房門照片，只見門上赫然出現<span class=\"red\">習近平肖像，還在下方插了兩根五星旗，照片上更以中文寫著「壞鬼在這間房間不受歡迎」</span>，艾斯尼班納蘭還加上註解，<span class=\"red\">「我們在台北居住的飯店門口，回答了中國人對我們台灣之行的威脅」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n艾斯尼班納蘭於昨（10日）在推特發文表示，自己看見中共官媒《中國日報》提到，<span class=\"red\">陪同捷克參議院議長韋德齊訪台的每一位成員都將被禁止進入中國，但他想一想自己仍然可以隨時到台灣，這不正是一個無可辯駁的證據，「證明一個中國根本不存在」</span>，更隨文附上諷刺漫畫，戰力十足。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Lem_Aschenbrenn/status/1304044859192418304?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLem_Aschenbrenn%2Fstatus%2F1304044859192418304%3Fs%3D20&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=801e60a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLem_Aschenbrenn%2Fstatus%2F1304044859192418304%3Fs%3D20&h=a5d7440b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Lem_Aschenbrenn/status/1304044859192418304?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/11/phpseddEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F11%2FphpseddEz.jpg&h=27b751af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n艾斯尼班納蘭（圖右）隨捷克參議院議長韋德齊（圖左）訪台。（擷取自Lum&iacute;r Aschenbrenner臉書）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3288474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3288474&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=a95c1a76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3288474&h=81702ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3288474</a>"},{"pid":"97d9b80a44f970ff3540961baa9c22a3c943241c","tid":2197951,"uid":3223,"like":372,"dislike":2,"score":370,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"他在推特發文表示，自己將被禁止進入中國，但他卻可以隨時到台灣，「這證明一個中國根本不存在」。<br />\n<br />\n啱喎"},{"pid":"e5f9eecd94631a2cef0c0ea6ea49e029887dae8d","tid":2197951,"uid":337052,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EhjlxkFXgAEiINK?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEhjlxkFXgAEiINK%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=2155829f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc754865d74f03e0602ef471387e39a0dbc03bb8","tid":2197951,"uid":60145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"8246976de0910af81939e4ec1b82351379c0c84d","tid":2197951,"uid":11097,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"又撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4de8eedc04ae69606ddfd14e581aba3f544a093","tid":2197951,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa